<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَاهًا لِذَيَّاكَ السَّمَاعِ فَكَمْ بِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لِلْقَلْبِ مِنْ طَرَبٍ وَمِنْ أَشْجَانِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَا ظَنَّ سَامِعُهُ بِصَوْتِ أَطْيَبِ الْـ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَصْوَاتِ مِنْ حُورِ الْجِنَانِ حِسَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>نَحْنُ النَّوَاعِمُ وَالْخَوَالِدُ خَيَّرَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>تٌ كَامِلاتُ الْحُسْنِ وَالإِحْسَانِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لَسْنَا نَمُوتُ وَلا نَخَافُ وَمَا لَنَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سَخَطٌ وَلا ضَغَنٌ مِن الأَضْغَانِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>طُوبَى لِمَنْ كُنَّا لَهُ وَكَذَاكَ طُو<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بَى لِلَّذِي هُوَ حَظُّنَا لَفْظَانِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فِي ذَاكَ آثَارٌ رُوِينَ وَذِكْرُهَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فِي التِّرْمِذِيِّ وَمُعْجَمِ الطَّبَرَانِي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَرَوَاهُ يَحْيى شَيْخُ الأَوْزَاعِي تَفْـ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>سِيرًا لِلَفْظَةِ يُحْبَرُونَ أَغَانِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>نَزِّهْ سَمَاعَكَ إِنْ أَرَدْتَ سَمَاعَ ذَيَّـ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>ـاكَ الْغِنَا عَنْ هَذِهِ الأَلْحَانِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لا تُؤْثِرِ الأَدْنَى عَلَى الأَعْلَى فَتُحْـ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>رَمُ ذَا وَذَا يَا ذِلَّةَ الْحُرْمَانِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>